            <strong id="68">What is a Golden torrent?</strong>
            <p><a class="altlink" href="/torrents/?searchbox=&search=Search&golden=1">Torrents with a golden chest</a> (<img src="./images/golden.gif">) are considered "free leech", which means downloading them will not affect your download stats, but uploading on a golden torrent will still count towards your upload stats. This means that your ratio can only get better when downloading golden torrents. They are a great place to start for new users worried about their ratio.</p>
            <p>Note: <b>Golden torrents don't give you the right to hit-and-run</b>, you must seed them just as you would any other torrent.</p>
